  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study is evaluate the effect of uni-axial versus multidirectional balance
      training on muscle reaction time in subjects with chronic ankle instability. Muscle reaction
      time is measured on a trapdoor simulating an inversion sprain before and after a 6 week
      lasting balance training protocol.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
